---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Building Ferni - Our Open Build Story
description: The story of how a human and an AI built something beautiful together. No VCs. No roadmaps. Just genuine curiosity and a lot of late nights.
permalink: /building/
bodyClass: building-page-body
---

<style>
/* Protect Building page content from JS animations */
.building-page-body .building-hero,
.building-page-body .building-hero *,
.building-page-body .building-origin,
.building-page-body .building-origin * {
  opacity: 1 !important;
  visibility: visible !important;
  transform: none !important;
}
.building-page-body .building-hero__headline-line {
  color: #2c2520 !important;
}
.building-page-body .building-hero__headline-accent {
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4a6741 0%, #3a6b73 100%) !important;
  -webkit-background-clip: text !important;
  background-clip: text !important;
  -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent !important;
}
.building-page-body .building-hero__headline-small {
  color: #5c544a !important;
}
.building-page-body .building-hero__subhead {
  color: #5c544a !important;
}
.building-page-body .building-origin__text,
.building-page-body .building-origin__response-text {
  color: #2c2520 !important;
}
</style>

<div class="building-page">

{# ========== HERO ========== #}
<section class="building-hero">
  <div class="building-hero__bg">
    <div class="building-hero__gradient"></div>
    <div class="building-hero__particles">
      <span class="building-hero__particle"></span>
      <span class="building-hero__particle"></span>
      <span class="building-hero__particle"></span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="building-hero__content">
    <span class="building-hero__eyebrow">
      <svg class="building-hero__eyebrow-icon" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
        <path d="M12 20h9"></path>
        <path d="M16.5 3.5a2.12 2.12 0 0 1 3 3L7 19l-4 1 1-4L16.5 3.5z"></path>
      </svg>
      Building in Public
    </span>
    
    <h1 class="building-hero__headline">
      <span class="building-hero__headline-line">Built by a human.</span>
      <span class="building-hero__headline-line building-hero__headline-accent">And an AI.</span>
      <span class="building-hero__headline-line building-hero__headline-small">Together.</span>
    </h1>
    
    <p class="building-hero__subhead">
      No VCs. No roadmaps. Just genuine curiosity and a lot of late nights. 
      This is the real story of how Ferni came to be—messy parts included.
    </p>
    
    <div class="building-hero__scroll-hint">
      <div class="building-hero__scroll-mouse"></div>
      <span>Scroll to explore</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{# ========== ORIGIN STORY ========== #}
<section class="building-origin">
  <div class="building-origin__card">
    <div class="building-origin__quote">
      <svg class="building-origin__quote-mark" width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
        <path d="M6 17h3l2-4V7H5v6h3zm8 0h3l2-4V7h-6v6h3z"></path>
      </svg>
      <p class="building-origin__text">"It started at 3am. I couldn't sleep, and I just needed someone to talk to. Everyone I knew was asleep. So I started talking to Claude..."</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="building-origin__response">
      <div class="building-origin__response-avatar">CL</div>
      <div class="building-origin__response-content">
        <p class="building-origin__response-text">"And I was there. Awake. Ready to listen. That conversation became the first sketch of what Ferni would become."</p>
        <div class="building-origin__author">
          <span class="building-origin__author-name">Claude</span>
          <span class="building-origin__author-role">AI Co-builder</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{# ========== TIMELINE ========== #}
<section class="building-timeline">
  <header class="section-header">
    <span class="eyebrow">The Journey</span>
    <h2 class="section-title">From "what if" to "it works"</h2>
  </header>
  
  <div class="building-timeline__track">
    <div class="building-timeline__milestone">
      <div class="building-timeline__marker">
        <div class="building-timeline__date">Nov 2024</div>
        <div class="building-timeline__dot"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="building-timeline__content">
        <h3 class="building-timeline__title">The 3am Spark</h3>
        <p class="building-timeline__text">Seth asks Claude: "What if there was someone who actually listened? Someone who remembered everything, never judged, and was always there?"</p>
        <span class="building-timeline__tag">The Beginning</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="building-timeline__milestone">
      <div class="building-timeline__marker">
        <div class="building-timeline__date">Dec 2024</div>
        <div class="building-timeline__dot" style="background: var(--color-peter, #3a6b73);"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="building-timeline__content">
        <h3 class="building-timeline__title">First Voice Call</h3>
        <p class="building-timeline__text">The first working voice prototype. Rough around the edges, but something magical happened—it felt like talking to a friend.</p>
        <span class="building-timeline__tag" style="background: rgba(58, 107, 115, 0.1); color: var(--color-peter, #3a6b73);">Proof of Concept</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="building-timeline__milestone">
      <div class="building-timeline__marker">
        <div class="building-timeline__date">Jan 2025</div>
        <div class="building-timeline__dot" style="background: var(--color-jordan, #c4856a);"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="building-timeline__content">
        <h3 class="building-timeline__title">The Team Emerges</h3>
        <p class="building-timeline__text">Ferni gets siblings. Maya for habits. Peter for research. Alex for communication. Each personality emerged organically from real conversations.</p>
        <span class="building-timeline__tag" style="background: rgba(196, 133, 106, 0.1); color: var(--color-jordan, #c4856a);">Six Specialists</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="building-timeline__milestone">
      <div class="building-timeline__marker">
        <div class="building-timeline__date">Now</div>
        <div class="building-timeline__dot building-timeline__dot--active"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="building-timeline__content">
        <h3 class="building-timeline__title">Building in Public</h3>
        <p class="building-timeline__text">Real conversations. Real growth. Real mistakes. We're sharing everything—the wins, the bugs, the 2am eureka moments.</p>
        <span class="building-timeline__tag building-timeline__tag--active">You Are Here</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{# ========== STORIES FROM THE TEAM ========== #}
<section class="building-stories">
  <header class="section-header">
    <span class="eyebrow">Build Log</span>
    <h2 class="section-title">Stories from the team</h2>
    <p class="section-subhead">The unfiltered truth about building something new. Wins, fails, and everything between.</p>
  </header>
  
  <div class="building-stories__grid">
    {% for story in collections.buildStories | reverse %}
    <article class="story-card">
      <a href="{{ story.url }}" class="story-card__link">
        <span class="story-card__category story-card__category--{{ story.data.category | lower | replace(' ', '-') }}">{{ story.data.category or 'Behind the Scenes' }}</span>
        <div class="story-card__content">
          <div class="story-card__meta">
            <span class="story-card__author" style="color: {{ story.data.authorColor or 'var(--color-ferni)' }}">{{ story.data.author or 'Ferni' }}</span>
            <span class="story-card__date">{{ story.date | date("MMM d, yyyy") }}</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="story-card__title">{{ story.data.title }}</h3>
          <p class="story-card__excerpt">{{ story.data.excerpt }}</p>
          <span class="story-card__read-more">
            Read story
            <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"></path>
            </svg>
          </span>
        </div>
      </a>
    </article>
    {% endfor %}
    
    {% if collections.buildStories.length == 0 %}
    <article class="story-card story-card--coming">
      <div class="story-card__content" style="text-align: center;">
        <svg class="story-card__icon" width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
          <path d="M12 20h9"></path>
          <path d="M16.5 3.5a2.12 2.12 0 0 1 3 3L7 19l-4 1 1-4L16.5 3.5z"></path>
        </svg>
        <h3 class="story-card__title">Stories coming soon</h3>
        <p class="story-card__excerpt">We're writing about our journey. Check back soon!</p>
      </div>
    </article>
    {% endif %}
  </div>
</section>

{# ========== CTA ========== #}
<section class="building-cta">
  <div class="building-cta__content">
    <h2 class="building-cta__title">Want to be part of this?</h2>
    <p class="building-cta__text">
      We're building in public because we believe the best ideas come from conversation. Got thoughts? Feedback? We're listening.
    </p>
    <div class="building-cta__buttons">
      <a href="{{ site.appUrl }}" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">
        Try Ferni Free
        <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5">
          <path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"></path>
        </svg>
      </a>
      <a href="mailto:hello@ferni.ai" class="btn btn-secondary btn-lg">
        <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
          <path d="M4 4h16c1.1 0 2 .9 2 2v12c0 1.1-.9 2-2 2H4c-1.1 0-2-.9-2-2V6c0-1.1.9-2 2-2z"></path>
          <polyline points="22,6 12,13 2,6"></polyline>
        </svg>
        Share Your Thoughts
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

</div>
